I want you to identify the would be codon with the mutation by selecting which

00:01:42.080 --> 00:01:44.850
region you think it's in here. And then determine the

00:01:44.850 --> 00:01:48.210
type of coding region mutation that it is by selecting

00:01:48.210 --> 00:01:52.340
silent, missense, or nonsense. Remember, use your genetic code if

